class H{static lcase="abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz";static ucase="ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ";static numb="1234567890";static symbols="!@#$%?&*";static randRange(D=0,F=100){var A=F-D,z=Math.ceil(Math.log2(A)/8);if(!z)return D;var k=Math.pow(256,z),j=new Uint8Array(z);while(!0){window.crypto.getRandomValues(j);var T=0;for(var R=0;R<z;R++)T=(T<<8)+j[R];if(T<k-k%A)return D+T%A}}static generate(D=20,F=!0,A=!0,z=!0){let k=[];for(let j=0;j<D;j++)k.push(this.lcase.charAt(this.randRange(0,this.lcase.length)));if(F){let j=this.randRange(1,Math.floor(D/2)+1);for(let T=0;T<j;T++)k[this.randRange(0,k.length)]=this.ucase.charAt(this.randRange(0,this.ucase.length))}if(A){let j=this.randRange(1,Math.floor(D/2)+1);for(let T=0;T<j;T++)k[this.randRange(0,k.length)]=this.numb.charAt(this.randRange(0,this.numb.length))}if(z){let j=this.randRange(1,3);for(let T=0;T<j;T++)k[this.randRange(0,k.length)]=this.symbols.charAt(this.randRange(0,this.symbols.length))}return k.join("")}}var U=function(D){return Date.now()-D},K=document.getElementById("perf"),L=document.getElementById("result"),S=document.getElementById("amount"),J=document.getElementById("length"),M=document.getElementById("upperCase"),O=document.getElementById("numbers"),Q=document.getElementById("symbols");if(L)L.innerText=H.generate();document.getElementById("length")?.addEventListener("change",()=>{const D=document.getElementById("label-length");if(J&&D)D.innerText=J.value});document.getElementById("generate")?.addEventListener("click",()=>{if(!J||!M||!O||!Q||!L)return;const D=parseInt(J.value,10),F=M.checked,A=O.checked,z=Q.checked;L.innerText=H.generate(D,F,A,z)});document.getElementById("btn-start")?.addEventListener("click",()=>{if(!S||!K||!J||!M||!O||!Q)return;const D=parseInt(J.value,10),F=M.checked,A=O.checked,z=Q.checked;let k=parseInt(S.value,10);if(k<1)k=1;if(k>1e5)k=1e5;K.innerText="1. Performance test has started.\n";const j=Date.now();for(let T=0;T<k;T++)H.generate(D,F,A,z);K.innerText+="2. "+k+" random passwords generated in "+U(j)+" milliseconds.\n",K.innerText+="3. Performance test has completed in "+U(j)+" milliseconds.\n"});
